 "title": "Prison Break Gone Wrong",
 "summary": "At a makeshift 100-by-100-meter detention center, Captain Stone oversees caged prisoners as a chaotic prison break erupts. Convicts and soldiers clash in a brutal firefight, the desperate Comdore slinking to a broken door to fire on a dark Jedi and Zhaoan riflemen while squads of marines under Vengan push through breaches into the courtyard. Amid the gunfire, some convicts try to bolt for freedom even into the wilderness, but the assault grinds forward as the breakout descends into bloody confusion. The log captures a prison break that goes badly wrong for all involved.",
